&lt;p&gt;Degreed&#39;s platform reaches millions of learners worldwide — and the UI you build is how they experience it. As a Staff UI Engineer, you&#39;ll set the technical direction for a web application that needs to be accessible, scalable, and ready for what&#39;s next, including AI.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You&#39;ll work across teams, shape shared standards, and be the kind of engineer who makes everyone around them better. If you&#39;re driven by craft, ownership, and real impact at scale, this is where that energy belongs.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
